Furniture E-Commerce Website Fullstack Project

*** Update - Currently, switching Monolithic applications into Micro Service Architecture with TypeScript, 
Rabbitmq, Atlas MongoDB Cloud Database Service, Docker, Kubernetes, Redis

Furniture E-Commerce Website Fullstack Project. This website was built in SPA React Framework and Monolithic Server-side Application with Node.js.
Also, it allows make a payment through stripe api and console screen. Please test with card num 4242-4242-4242-4242 02/22.
By completing payment with your email, a confirmation of purchase or refund mail will be sent in minutes

Frontend - React, Redux, Hooks, HTML, SASS

Backend - Node.js, Express.js, Sendgrid, Stripe

Database - Redis, MongoDB(Atlas)

Deployment - Heroku Cloud Platform
